# Bug Investigation

- Start from the first root cause, not the last cascading error.
- For Nextflow failures, read upward from the bottom of `nextflow.log`.
- For template syntax/runtime failures, inspect generated `.command.sh`.
- Classify the bug as DSL2, config, template rendering, container runtime, launcher, CI, docs/schema, or fixture data.
- Add a targeted regression check when practical and record what was verified.
